text: Héctor Eduardo Pérez Cuevas (born 16 June 1991) is a Venezuelan footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Aragua F.C. in the Venezuelan Primera División. ==References== ==External links== *Profile at Ceroacero Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Asociación Civil Deportivo Lara players Category:Trujillanos FC players Category:Atlético Socopó players Category:Aragua FC players Category:Venezuelan Primera División players Category:Venezuelan footballers Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:People from Acarigua
